<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Minha Rede Social</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: white;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #1e293b;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .post {
      background: #1e293b;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .user {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #60a5fa;
    }

    .like {
      margin-top: 10px;
      background: #2563eb;
      border: none;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .like:hover {
      background: #1d4ed8;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <h1>🚀 Minha Rede Social</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="post">
      <div class="user">@joao</div>
      <p>Começando minha nova rede social 😎</p>
      <button class="like">Curtir ❤️</button>
    </div>

    <div class="post">
      <div class="user">@maria</div>
      <p>Isso aqui tá ficando interessante 🔥</p>
      <button class="like">Curtir ❤️</button>
    </div>

    <div class="post">
      <div class="user">@você</div>
      <p>Meu primeiro post na plataforma 🚀</p>
      <button class="like">Curtir ❤️</button>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
